values.summary:
Facilitate Continuous Improvement initiatives at Four Lakes Label, a division of Western States, emphasizing the importance of having a respectful, inclusive, and forward thinking culture;
Educate team members on Lean concepts and problem solving tools through projects that focus on eliminating waste and growing the company;
A synopsis of recent initiatives: reduced the setup and run time between cycle changes on one of our machines, resulting in a savings of $9000 annually; reduced waste in shipping label material by $3500 annually; leading a team focused on developing new, standardized training materials across the organization; leading a team that will digitize the flow of our order information, resulting in $49,830 direct savings and $43,000 indirect savings annually with a project investment of only $2300 (ROI 15 days)
